(676, 307, 280, 'Boitumelo Masuge', 'Amen Katli I really thank God for this group, it makes me to grow in faith nd to trust God more. I really love ds devotion. To be still before God means " ur will oh God not my will", is allowing the Heavenly Trinity to act on ur behalf. U become to see things with the spiritual eye nd nothing matters bt the will of God.', '', '2012-08-22 18:18:48'),
