(707, 157, 274, 'Nelson', 'I will share with you this brother Daniel, personally, I would like God to involve and make way for me in the political field and governance. I am getting to that stage...', '', '2012-08-26 18:41:30'),
(708, 307, 282, 'Boitumelo Masuge', 'Wow tnx saints for ur comments. Indeed were stepping forward nd showing the world wat we were made of. I''m so blessed by this devotion. We must practice wat we read in the word of God cause ds word is alive nd real nd it produces good results as long as we practice it.', '', '2012-08-26 19:46:59'),
(709, 66, 283, 'Patricia Mthembu', 'Men are also welcome to participate in this devotion, for we are one in Christ Jesus.', '', '2012-08-27 06:35:40'),
(710, 82, 282, 'Kt - Katlego Pelle', 'This is powerful Boitumelo. And there''s something that we need to understand; When you speak something, it happens immediately in the spirit even though it might manifest later in the flesh. When Jesus spoke to a tree and said, "no one will eat from you again", the tree started dying from that point even though the death signs were not yet evident. The next day Peter realized that the tree had withered. Notice something here: the tree did not die the next day, it died by the time Jesus said no one will ever eat from it. This is the power of words. With our word, yes we can change situations. Thanks Boitumelo.', '', '2012-08-27 18:09:48'),
(711, 82, 274, 'Kt - Katlego Pelle', 'Nelson, I believe Mr. Delayypo has said a ''mouth-full''. Nelson, concerning your vision of going into the political field and governance, I feel in my spirit that this is part of what you were born for. We really need committed Christians in those fields. And hey, with the name you have "Nelson" I can tell you''ll be a good leader, Mr Mandela Sir.', '', '2012-08-27 18:20:11'),
(712, 307, 282, 'Boitumelo Masuge', 'Amen brother Katlego. Ds is so true. Nothing is impossible with our God. I like the fact that wen we speak, in the realm something is happening. If we cn abide wt that rule, we shall never struggle abt a thing.', '', '2012-08-27 18:34:31'),
(713, 307, 283, 'Boitumelo Masuge', 'Amen aus pat. U hav said it all. Dts Y God said we shud submit because He knew dt we dnt struggle to love. Women r honered by the Lord, without them men are incomplete. They play a big role in the world.', '', '2012-08-27 18:59:15'),
(714, 82, 282, 'Kt - Katlego Pelle', 'Exactly. Christians, we should mature to a point where we don''t rely on physical evidence but rely fully on the truth we know in the Spirit.', '', '2012-08-27 19:10:42'),
(715, 102, 283, 'Rose Joubert', 'Thank you so so much Patricia for writing a message on us "women". Personally I believe that being a woman is a gift from God. Let us treasure, honour and respect this marvelous gift of being women.', '', '2012-08-28 05:23:32'),
(716, 69, 283, 'Mpho Dlamini', 'Amen. Thank you Sis Patricia for making us aware of the incredible power found in us.', '', '2012-08-28 08:07:40'),
(717, 90, 283, 'Daniel Delayapo', 'Praise the Lord. Women we salute you. For you are the ones who raised us up and taught us how things are done. You are the channels through which God brings new lives to earth. We salute you Mamas, we Salute you.', '', '2012-08-28 08:11:20'),
(718, 90, 282, 'Daniel Delayapo', 'That''s right, we also have the creative power which is in the mouth of God. We can shape our lives with our words.', '', '2012-08-28 08:26:54'),
(719, 90, 274, 'Daniel Delayapo', 'Hello again guys. Nelson I agree with Kt below here, your passion says it all. One thing I can say to you is that never lose that passion, keep on trusting God and he will make a way for you. We really need leaders who inquire from the Lord. I will also start praying for you Nelson, one thing I love about prayer is that it has No barriers.', '', '2012-08-28 09:02:37'),
(720, 82, 274, 'Kt - Katlego Pelle', 'Now that is one of the ways of how we influence culture, by having Christian leaders within governmental organizations, these Christian leaders will then implement Kingdom rules in governance. I love this.', '', '2012-08-28 09:12:09'),
