(722, 112, 284, 'Joshua Nkoe', 'Powerful brother KT.Faith agrees with God and shuts the door on the devil.You can never achieve the impossible if you never attempt the impossible.Jesus said to the blind men,"...According to your faith be it unto you "(Matthew 9:29).And their eyes were opened.The Word of God is faith Food.Hallelujah !!', '', '2012-08-28 21:10:09'),
