(972, 82, 320, 'Kt - Katlego Pelle', 'One thing I love about prayer is that there are no barriers to it. Our prayers as the church can intervene in governmental decision making. Let''s stand in the gap as the Bible calls us Kings & Priests.', '', '2012-10-01 14:10:28'),
