(1056, 82, 346, 'Kt - Katlego Pelle', 'The fact that even future sins have been forgiven simply means that Jesus would never change His mind about us, OR that there is nothing that can cause Jesus to change His mind about us. This is amazing Love.', '', '2012-11-05 06:59:05'),
